OL,3,CHow football's financial rules
OL,4,Cencouraged Midlands clubs to sell
OL,5,Clocal heroes
OL,7,FIn a different time, Aston Villa could
OL,8,Fbe riding a wave and cementing
OL,9,Fthemselves as a contender for the
OL,10,FPremier League title.
OL,12,FThe success of reaching the quarter-
OL,13,Ffinals of the Champions League would
OL,14,Ftempt their wealthy owners into buying
OL,15,Fthe best players to compete regularly
OL,16,Fon that stage.
OL,18,FThat can't happen now because of
OL,19,FProfit and Sustainability Rules (PSR)
OL,20,Fthat are well intentioned, but are in
OL,21,Fsome cases throttling ambition.
