OL,3,CHow football's financial rules
OL,4,Cencouraged Midlands clubs to sell
OL,5,Clocal heroes
OL,7,FIt is all based on revenue, so a club
OL,8,Fthe size of Manchester United can
OL,9,Ffinish 15th but still blow Villa out
OL,10,Fof the water, even though Unai Emery's
OL,11,Fside finished 6th.
OL,13,FThis summer United spent over #200m on
OL,14,Fplayers, whilst Villa scraped around
OL,15,Ffor loans and spent less than #30m. At
OL,16,Fthat rate, it will not take long for
OL,17,FUnited to overtake and there is next
OL,18,Fto nothing that Villa's owners can do
OL,19,Fabout it.
