OL,3,CHow football's financial rules
OL,4,Cencouraged Midlands clubs to sell
OL,5,Clocal heroes
OL,7,FDamian Vidagany, Villa's Director of
OL,8,FFootball Operations posted on X once
OL,9,Fthe window closed: "The clubs with
OL,10,Frevenues and no results, they spend
OL,11,Ffast and spend stronger to wipe us
OL,12,Ffrom (the) top."
OL,14,FThe other harsh reality of PSR rules
OL,15,Fis that it's encouraging a league of
OL,16,Fplayers with little or no connection
OL,17,Fto the club they play for. It is much
OL,18,Fmore profitable to sell a star who has
OL,19,Fcome through the academy because it
OL,20,Fgoes through as pure profit on the
OL,21,Fbooks.
