OL,3,CHow football's financial rules
OL,4,Cencouraged Midlands clubs to sell
OL,5,Clocal heroes
OL,7,FWe've seen that with Jacob Ramsey at
OL,8,FVilla who was sold to Newcastle
OL,9,FUnited. A club, ironically, who have
OL,10,Fsimilar issues with PSR.
OL,12,FElsewhere, West Bromwich Albion sold
OL,13,FTom Fellows to Southampton for #10m.
OL,14,FLeicester City sold Kasey McAteer to
OL,15,FIpswich and Stoke City sold 18-year-
OL,16,Fold Sol Sidibe to PSV Eindhoven.
