OL,3,CHow football's financial rules
OL,4,Cencouraged Midlands clubs to sell
OL,5,Clocal heroes
OL,7,FThere are exceptions in the Midlands,
OL,8,FNottingham Forest were able to spend
OL,9,F#100m because of the increased revenue
OL,10,Fthey expect from qualifying for the
OL,11,FEuropa League.
OL,13,FThe big question there is if head
OL,14,Fcoach Nuno Espirito Santo is happy
OL,15,Fwith the new players? Sporting
OL,16,FDirector Edu has made his mark with
OL,17,Fthese signings but Nuno's recent
OL,18,Fcomments suggest he hasn't been as
OL,19,Finvolved as he would like.
