OL,3,CHow football's financial rules
OL,4,Cencouraged Midlands clubs to sell
OL,5,Clocal heroes
OL,7,FThis is also a small window of
OL,8,Fopportunity. Forest have been burnt
OL,9,Fbefore and got a points deduction last
OL,10,Fyear for breaching PSR. They will
OL,11,Falways be close to the line.
OL,13,FBirmingham City are also current
OL,14,Fwinners with the PSR rules. That's
OL,15,Fbecause of the season they spent in
OL,16,FLeague One. The rules in that league
OL,17,Fare different and mean owners can pump
OL,18,Fin more money.
