OL,3,CHow football's financial rules
OL,4,Cencouraged Midlands clubs to sell
OL,5,Clocal heroes
OL,7,FBlues spent more on Jay Stansfield
OL,8,Fthan Stoke City have spent in three
OL,9,Fwindows.
OL,11,FStoke are arguably the biggest losers
OL,12,Fof PSR because of the gap between how
OL,13,Fwealthy their owners are and how much
OL,14,Frevenue the club generates.
OL,16,FThe mood appears to be shifting on PSR
OL,17,Fand changes may well come. Perhaps
OL,18,Fthen a Midlands club will appeal more
OL,19,Fthan those who were in the right place
OL,20,Fat the right time.
